gobblin.data.management.retention.policy

Class PredicateRetentionPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.retention.policy.PredicateRetentionPolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RetentionPolicy<DatasetVersion>

    public class PredicateRetentionPolicy
extends Object
implements RetentionPolicy<DatasetVersion>
    Implementation of RetentionPolicy that marks a DatasetVersion for deletion if it does not pass a specified Predicate. The Predicate class is determined by the key RETENTION_POLICY_PREDICATE_CLASS.
